column5: Water is very low, saw some rocks I didn't know where there. Water is also still warm, all though we marked many big fish nothing was biting, and that goes for all the boats (6)out there. Few more weeks and some cold weather, and a few less nets this year could make things interesting.
Will second that...only rough fish to be had (ie. Silver Bass) being caught. Let's hope it is not too far around the corner!
